 1.000    MyXi_c*+ pi-         PHSP ; ## Xic(2815)0 -> Xic*+ pi- 
Enddecay
CDecay Myanti-Xi_c*0

Decay MyXi_c*+
 1.000    MyXi_c0  pi+         PHSP ;
Enddecay
CDecay Myanti-Xi_c*-

Decay Mya_1+
